title: 47. Rules Young Entrepreneurs MUST Follow
itunes:title: 47. Rules Young Entrepreneurs MUST Follow
description: Starting a business and building your personal brand is an extremely difficult uphill battle. It requires a lot of confidence mixed with grit, determination, and endurance to come out victorious. On today's episode, Andy tells you how you can avoid the foolish mistakes when starting your journey to building your empire.
